üéØ CCEE QUICK MEMORY POINTS
Symmetric = same key, fast (AES, DES)
Asymmetric = public/private key, slow (RSA, ECC)
Protocols (SSL/TLS) use BOTH
Asymmetric ‚Üí key exchange
Symmetric ‚Üí bulk data encryption
